title: SwifTEA: Inside Scoop From The ATW Short Film Premiere
description:
It happened. A Swiftie got a DM from TaylorNation, and it was an invite to a secret session. Why was she a chosen one? And what happened at this secret premiere? And what was it like to witness the first ever live performance of the 10 minute version of All Too Well? Natalia reveals all! Be sure to check out more Swiftie content on her TikTok, @swiftiecult.
What would you like to hear from us? Lots of ways to reach us!
